Overview 
This role will lead the architecting, implementation, and ongoing refinement of our core business applications (eCommerce, ERP, CRM, Support and Field Operations, Middleware). The VP of MIS will collaborate with the business leaders on the transaction, reporting, and analytics tools to scale the business, reduce cycle times and improve the total cost of ownership. This role requires an in-depth knowledge of the business operations as it will help design and implement the end-to-end systems that enable key business solutions such as bundling of SaaS subscription and physical product sales and fulfillment, marketplace platform, 360-degree view of the customer, omni-channel marketing, and sales, and leading-edge supply chain models. The MIS platforms we are developing are scalable and flexible, enabling the business to be agile, such as rapidly onboarding partners and acquisitions. 
 
